.\" Manpage for weather.
.TH man 1 "25 February 2022" "1.0" "weather man page"
.SH NAME
.B weather
- a weather finder for any city in the world
.SH VERSION
1.0
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B weather
[city from which you want to get the weather]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B weather
is a command that allows finding the weather of any city in the world in a fast way
.SH OPTIONS
No options available for this version
.SH NOTE
When no arguments are passed to the command, it will display the weather in your location - It 
may be approximate
.SH BUGS
No known bugs
.SH AUTHOR
.B Haroune Hassine
